title: About
content:
Hello! My name is Skye and I am an indpendent photographer from Colorado. I have always enjoyed how photography captures a moment in time that will never happen again, making it special.
I do commisions for photographs, much of my rate is negotiable and I would love to work with you! Check out the Work section to see some examples of my work.
My email is skyebonial@gmail.com, if you get in touch make sure to tell me why you are emailing -- thanks!
